:3,"flags":0,"comment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eWell, this isn't exactly \"news\":\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSocial media guidelines\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nThe name and handle of your social media account and any and all pages cannot begin with a Mastodon word mark, or a similar mark (e.g. \"mastodoon\", \"mast0don\", \"mstdn\"). In addition, Mastodon logos cannot be used in a way that might suggest affiliation with or endorsement by Mastodon.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e—— \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/mastodon/joinmastodon/commit/020d62dc2df5b8a65abe9562631397ce16ed4d8f#diff-5d601b708be2b031188d61b2902f5d210ec77d4588439666bb56df6b6a0b866aR55\" rel=\"ugc\"\u003ehttps://github.com/mastodon/joinmastodon/~\u003c/a\u003e (2022)\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBut this is the first time they've included proactive reminders within the software.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Well, this isn't exactly \"news\":\r\n\r\n\u003e **Social media guidelines**  \r\n\u003e The name and handle of your social media account and any and all pages cannot begin with a Mastodon word mark, or a similar mark (e.g. \"mastodoon\", \"mast0don\", \"mstdn\"). In addition, Mastodon logos cannot be used in a way that might suggest affiliation with or endorsement by Mastodon.\r\n\r\n—— [https://github.com/mastodon/joinmastodon/~](https://github.com/mastodon/joinmastodon/commit/020d62dc2df5b8a65abe9562631397ce16ed4d8f#diff-5d601b708be2b031188d61b2902f5d210ec77d4588439666bb56df6b6a0b866aR55) (2022)\r\n\r\nBut this is the first time they've included proactive reminders within the software.","submitter_user":"cxplay","user_is_author":false,"tags":["distributed"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/0qggzn","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/0qggzn/mastodon_don_t_use_mastodon_mstdn_domain"},{"short_id":"xkxbq3","created_at":"2026-04-16T04:56:15.000-05:00","title":"I Let Claude Opus Write a Chrome Exploit: T